name: WELCOME #TEIA
description:
My interpretation of the new logo for @TeiaCommunity - Pixel lettering; My logo idea is to keep only the first "T" which could be handy as profile picture, with room to make it rounded and versatile for different platforms. It can also be designed as whole all caps font to use in different situations and purposes.

First @natived_ mint on Teia celebrating and testing the platform.
Made a mockup and put it together as a gif. Much love goes to all the community.
